%% Data Flow Diagram - lm-evaluation-harness
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Job as LMEval Job Pod<br/>User 65532:65532
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ModelAPI as Remote Model API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OCIReg as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>output/

    Note over Operator,FS: Flow 1: Local Model Evaluation
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job (LMEvalJob CRD)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Job: Schedule Pod
    Job->>HFHub: Download model & datasets<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>Job: Model weights + datasets
    Job->>Job: Run evaluation tasks<br/>(local inference)
    Job->>FS: Write results (JSON)

    Note over Job,S3: Flow 2: S3-based Model + OCI Results
    Job->>S3: Download model weights<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (AccessKey/SecretKey)
    S3-->>Job: Model artifacts
    Job->>Job: Run evaluation tasks<br/>(local inference)
    Job->>OCIReg: Publish results (skopeo)<br/>Auth: Registry credentials
    OCIReg-->>Job: Push confirmation

    Note over Job,ModelAPI: Flow 3: Remote API Evaluation
    Job->>ModelAPI: POST inference request<br/>Auth: API Key (OpenAI/Anthropic/WatsonX)
    ModelAPI-->>Job: Model response
    Job->>Job: Score and aggregate results
    Job->>FS: Write results (JSON)
